photography company

1558
01:40:09,360 --> 01:40:11,480
and hiring a good photographer.

1559
01:40:12,020 --> 01:40:13,190
And here you are!

1560
01:40:13,860 --> 01:40:15,570
Don't think any further.
Let's collaborate!

1561
01:40:15,690 --> 01:40:17,690
-Well, I..
-Why? You don't want to collaborate?

1562
01:40:17,860 --> 01:40:18,980
I didn't mean that.

1563
01:40:18,980 --> 01:40:20,860
-I'm not a professional.
-That's not a problem.

1564
01:40:20,900 --> 01:40:22,220
And, we just met, right?

1565
01:40:22,220 --> 01:40:24,080
Yeah! We should have met
much earlier.

1566
01:40:24,110 --> 01:40:26,070
We got late.
I felt so too.

1567
01:40:29,110 --> 01:40:31,020
I have great contacts.

1568
01:40:32,190 --> 01:40:33,190
I'm serious.

1569
01:40:34,400 --> 01:40:36,740
We can cover at least four
or five weddings in a month.

1570
01:40:36,770 --> 01:40:38,480
I'll pay you Rs. 20,000
for each wedding.

1571
01:40:38,770 --> 01:40:39,770
What say?

1572
01:40:39,820 --> 01:40:42,070
-How much?
-Err... 20,000 Rupees.

1573
01:40:44,520 --> 01:40:46,480
Okay!
Twenty five!

1574
01:40:48,150 --> 01:40:50,820
Fine! 30,000.
Don't ask for more than that. Please!

1575
01:40:51,690 --> 01:40:52,730
I need to think about it.

1576
01:40:52,770 --> 01:40:54,610
Go ahead.
I'll be right here.

1577
01:40:56,110 --> 01:40:57,400
-Sir, ticket?
-I didn't buy it?

1578
01:40:57,440 --> 01:40:58,480
No.

1579
01:41:00,070 --> 01:41:01,190
I forgot!

1580
01:41:01,230 --> 01:41:03,320
I keep forgetting
things wherever I go.

1581
01:41:04,650 --> 01:41:06,150
You rascal! Even you managed
to get married?

1582
01:41:06,180 --> 01:41:07,220
Here!
Look over here!

1583
01:41:08,070 --> 01:41:09,230
-Hey!
-Move away!

1584
01:41:09,480 --> 01:41:10,650
Smile, please!

1585
01:41:11,440 --> 01:41:12,440
Who's that?

1586
01:41:13,360 --> 01:41:15,070
-Hey Sathish!
-Move away, you!

1587
01:41:16,270 --> 01:41:17,940
Don't crowd around.
Please move!

1588
01:41:18,330 --> 01:41:19,700
-Over here!
-Excuse me!

1589
01:41:22,840 --> 01:41:23,890
Smile, damn it!

1590
01:41:25,980 --> 01:41:27,150
Come on, stand here, you hag!

1591
01:41:27,190 --> 01:41:28,230
Get lost!

1592
01:41:29,440 --> 01:41:31,070
The feast is ready
at the dining hall.

1593
01:41:31,110 --> 01:41:32,230
After getting photos clicked,

1594
01:41:32,270 --> 01:41:34,020
all of you may proceed
to the dining hall.

1595
01:41:34,070 --> 01:41:35,820
Smile!
Smile!

1596
01:41:36,080 --> 01:41:38,710
And they shall become one.

1597
01:41:38,790 --> 01:41:40,830
Even if he is starving,
he should feed her.

1598
01:41:40,900 --> 01:41:42,150
Even if he is starving...

1599
01:41:42,570 --> 01:41:43,570
Feed, feed!

1600
01:41:51,640 --> 01:41:52,970
-Please! Just one!
-Get lost!

1601
01:42:04,190 --> 01:42:05,190
-Phew!
-Oops!

1602
01:42:05,360 --> 01:42:06,400
Careful!

1603
01:42:07,360 --> 01:42:08,400
Hey!

1604
01:42:08,650 --> 01:42:09,650
What is this?

1605
01:42:10,430 --> 01:42:11,640
What kind of photos are these?

1606
01:42:12,870 --> 01:42:15,230
You've covered the groom's family
really well.

1607
01:42:15,520 --> 01:42:17,270
-We're the ones paying you, right?
-There's still more to pay.

1608
01:42:17,330 --> 01:42:19,040
-I'm the bride's mother, right?
-Yeah!

1609
01:42:19,070 --> 01:42:20,690
Have you clicked a single photo
of me smiling?

1610
01:42:20,700 --> 01:42:21,330
No.

1611
01:42:21,360 --> 01:42:23,110
What kind of photographer are you?

1612
01:42:24,930 --> 01:42:26,430
-What's your name?
-Jimmy!

1613
01:42:26,490 --> 01:42:27,490
Nice name!

1614
01:42:27,610 --> 01:42:28,730
Take this with you!

1615
01:42:28,820 --> 01:42:30,650
-But I..
-Just get lost!

1616
01:42:32,570 --> 01:42:33,690
What?

1617
01:42:35,410 --> 01:42:37,710
They think they can say anything
if they are paying us!

1618
01:42:37,730 --> 01:42:39,320
But they want
everything to be done!

1619
01:42:39,320 --> 01:42:40,820
It's a grand wedding, right?

1620
01:42:40,860 --> 01:42:43,150
Candid photography,
traditional photography...

1621
01:42:43,150 --> 01:42:44,610
Traditional with candid photography...

1622
01:42:44,610 --> 01:42:46,360
Helicam, Jimmy Jib and what not!

1623
01:42:46,940 --> 01:42:49,070
Where do I take all this?
To that town hall!

1624
01:42:49,090 --> 01:42:50,430
And that place has no AC or fridge!

1625
01:42:50,450 --> 01:42:51,830
I mean... no fans!

1626
01:42:52,070 --> 01:42:53,620
And there are those
saree-clad aunties,

1627
01:42:53,730 --> 01:42:55,850
sweating like they just took a steam bath.

1628
01:42:56,700 --> 01:42:59,370
Didn't that hag say that
there's no smiling photo of hers?

1629
01:42:59,490 --> 01:43:01,950
To make people smile when they don't,
have I learned morphing?

1630
01:43:02,200 --> 01:43:03,660
-Jimmy bro!
-What?

1631
01:43:04,030 --> 01:43:05,030
Come here.

1632
01:43:06,450 --> 01:43:07,950
What do you think
about these photos?

1633
01:43:09,620 --> 01:43:10,620
They are really nice.

1634
01:43:11,910 --> 01:43:14,410
They were clicked in Chennai
by a photographer named Danny

1635
01:43:14,450 --> 01:43:16,160
for a company called
'Weddings by Alpheus'.

1636
01:43:16,530 --> 01:43:18,410
This company doesn't
cover grand weddings.

1637
01:43:18,870 --> 01:43:20,890
They cover only small weddings
of people who are educated,

1638
01:43:20,920 --> 01:43:22,310
wise and mature enough.

1639
01:43:23,120 --> 01:43:25,740
With just immediate family members
and close friends in attendance,

1640
01:43:25,780 --> 01:43:26,950
Intimate weddings!

1641
01:43:28,380 --> 01:43:30,510
There's no brand which specializes
exclusively in intimate weddings,

1642
01:43:30,530 --> 01:43:31,660
currently in Kerala.

1643
01:43:32,030 --> 01:43:33,070
Why don't we start one?

1644
01:43:33,120 --> 01:43:34,820
Why not?
Let's start it today itself.

1645
01:43:35,120 --> 01:43:36,950
So that we can sit at home
from tomorrow.

1646
01:43:37,910 --> 01:43:39,160
Dude, what do you think?

1647
01:43:39,700 --> 01:43:42,530
You think weddings are conducted
in Kerala to get two people married?

1648
01:43:42,700 --> 01:43:44,450
A wedding here is a huge
celebratory event,

1649
01:43:44,490 --> 01:43:46,120
where people invite relatives,
friends and acquaintances...

1650
01:43:46,160 --> 01:43:47,490
... to show off their pomp and grandeur.

1651
01:43:47,530 --> 01:43:49,820
Take your intimate concept to
them and watch how they react!

1652
01:43:49,870 --> 01:43:51,530
-Sheesh!
-Jimmy bro!

1653
01:43:52,160 --> 01:43:55,280
Many people are reconsidering
the idea of having grand weddings.

1654
01:43:55,320 --> 01:43:57,240
Most Hindi actors are getting
married like this now.

1655
01:43:57,660 --> 01:43:59,200
Even our actor Prithviraj
got married like this!

1656
01:43:59,240 --> 01:44:00,450
Oh yeah!
Rajuettan is awesome!

1657
01:44:01,870 --> 01:44:03,870
If we target Kerala alone,
we'll be in a fix.

1658
01:44:04,280 --> 01:44:06,410
We should market our company
all over India.

1659
01:44:07,410 --> 01:44:08,620
If we start this now,

1660
01:44:09,280 --> 01:44:11,530
when intimate weddings
start trending in Kerala,

1661
01:44:11,620 --> 01:44:13,490
we will be the kings here!

1662
01:44:15,660 --> 01:44:18,410
Everyone is running
after grand weddings now.

1663
01:44:19,030 --> 01:44:21,910
Should we run along with them,
or ahead of them?

1664
01:44:22,280 --> 01:44:23,280
Think about it!

1665
01:44:31,530 --> 01:44:40,490
♪ Enough is enough
Speak to me with a smile ♪

1666
01:44:40,620 --> 01:44:44,620
♪ You inhabit my heart ♪

1667
01:44:44,620 --> 01:44:46,450
-Is this his new song?
-Yes.

1668
01:44:46,490 --> 01:44:50,070
♪ What is the use of running away? ♪

1669
01:44:50,450 --> 01:44:55,620
♪ You keep pulling me towards you
Using your magic ♪

1670
01:44:56,320 --> 01:44:57,700
The tea is very nice.

1671
01:44:57,700 --> 01:44:58,820
Just like your idea!

1672
01:45:00,030 --> 01:45:02,240
♪ You keep pulling me towards you
Using your magic ♪

1673
01:45:02,280 --> 01:45:04,030
How will we market
ourselves all over India?

1674
01:45:04,910 --> 01:45:06,370
-We needn't do anything.
-Then?

1675
01:45:06,490 --> 01:45:08,410
You see this guy?
Shall we make him do it?

1676
01:45:09,450 --> 01:45:11,120
-Prateek Tiwari?
-Yes.

1677
01:45:11,120 --> 01:45:12,950
Dude, he's a top singer in Bollywood.

1678
01:45:13,070 --> 01:45:15,570
He charges millions for an ad.
Don't you know all this?

1679
01:45:15,620 --> 01:45:17,620
-We needn't pay him in millions.
-How much, then?

1680
01:45:17,740 --> 01:45:19,240
Is 10,000 fine?

1681
01:45:19,280 --> 01:45:28,570
♪ Enough is enough
Speak to me with a smile ♪

1682
01:45:29,280 --> 01:45:30,950
Hey guys!
I'm in Mumbai.

1683
01:45:30,950 --> 01:45:32,240
And we're performing
here tonight.

1684
01:45:32,280 --> 01:45:33,780
So, please do come, see us.
Okay?

1685
01:45:34,200 --> 01:45:35,780
I have something to share
with you guys.

1686
01:45:35,950 --> 01:45:37,660
I have a friend, Arun Neelakandan.

1687
01:45:37,780 --> 01:45:40,240
And he's one of the best photographers
that I know personally.

1688
01:45:40,280 --> 01:45:41,990
Dude, he's hyping you up!

1689
01:45:42,160 --> 01:45:44,280
Now he's starting his own
wedding photography brand...

1690
01:45:44,320 --> 01:45:45,780
...called Blue Eye
Intimate Weddings.

1691
01:45:45,820 --> 01:45:46,820
Ours?

1692
01:45:46,870 --> 01:45:49,370
So, the first couple to book
their wedding with this brand,

1693
01:45:50,280 --> 01:45:52,160
I will sing at their wedding,

1694
01:45:52,240 --> 01:45:53,240
for free!

1695
01:45:53,530 --> 01:45:56,280
Did he say that he'll sing for free,
at our first wedding?

1696
01:45:56,410 --> 01:45:57,950
Did he just say free?
Are you sure?

1697
01:45:57,950 --> 01:46:00,030
-Prateek, I love you man!
-I love you too, dude!

1698
01:46:00,160 --> 01:46:01,240
Who is he?

1699
01:46:01,950 --> 01:46:02,950
He is my friend!

1700
01:46:05,570 --> 01:46:06,700
Friend?

1701
01:46:07,160 --> 01:46:08,160
Sure, sir.
Sure, sir.

1702
01:46:08,530 --> 01:46:09,570
We can do all that.

1703
01:46:09,870 --> 01:46:11,700
With that single video
from Prateek Tiwari...

1704
01:46:12,450 --> 01:46:15,740
we received around 20 wedding
enquiries in two days.

1705
01:46:16,120 --> 01:46:18,950
The most surprising fact was that
many of them were from Kerala.

1706
01:46:19,410 --> 01:46:21,200
If we get all this advance money,
we'll rock it!

1707
01:46:21,240 --> 01:46:22,450
Your idea is fantastic, man!

1708
01:46:25,820 --> 01:46:26,820
blueye10

1709
01:46:27,120 --> 01:46:28,490
Why is your email ID like this?

1710
01:46:28,820 --> 01:46:30,370
It's been like that since 10th grade.

1711
01:46:31,200 --> 01:46:32,450
My dad is my hero.

1712
01:46:33,030 --> 01:46:34,870
So I just modified my
dad's name a little bit.

1713
01:46:34,990 --> 01:46:36,120
Neelakandan.

1714
01:46:36,320 --> 01:46:37,410
Neela (blue) kan (eye) ten.

1715
01:46:37,780 --> 01:46:39,120
So creative!

1716
01:46:39,410 --> 01:46:40,780
Don't pull my leg, Jimmy bro!

1717
01:46:40,950 --> 01:46:41,990
What's your family name?

1718
01:46:42,120 --> 01:46:43,120
Is it Mangalassery?

1719
01:46:43,660 --> 01:46:44,950
-No!
-No?

1720
01:46:45,570 --> 01:46:46,870
-Not at all?
-No!

1721
01:47:04,780 --> 01:47:07,280
As I started covering weddings
of my choice,

1722
01:47:07,620 --> 01:47:10,620
I began enjoying wedding
photography thoroughly.

1723
01:47:11,370 --> 01:47:14,430
Framing, lighting,
composition, technique...

1724
01:47:14,450 --> 01:47:15,760
None of this mattered.

1725
01:47:15,780 --> 01:47:18,320
I gradually learnt that capturing
the hearts of the people before you,

1726
01:47:18,370 --> 01:47:19,820
is what photography is all about.

1727
01:47:20,870 --> 01:47:22,140
I started anticipating.

1728
01:47:22,870 --> 01:47:23,990
Happiness!

1729
01:47:24,200 --> 01:47:25,240
Sorrow!

1730
01:47:26,370 --> 01:47:27,660
Tears!

1731
01:47:28,450 --> 01:47:29,660
Celebrations!

1732
01:47:31,950 --> 01:47:33,160
Romp!

1733
01:47:35,280 --> 01:47:36,870
I was loving what I was doing.

1734
01:47:39,780 --> 01:47:42,070
The greatest attraction
of wedding photography...

1735
01:47:42,120 --> 01:47:43,320
is the freedom that we get.

1736
01:47:45,030 --> 01:47:47,700
We can keep clicking photos of all
the girls attending the wedding,

1737
01:47:47,700 --> 01:47:48,740
with no restrictions.

1738
01:47:51,620 --> 01:47:52,990
When we go for certain weddings,

1739
01:47:53,030 --> 01:47:54,780
we feel that the bride
is nothing...

1740
01:47:54,780 --> 01:47:57,330
in front of her cousins, friends
or bridesmaids. So many girls!

1741
01:47:57,700 --> 01:47:59,370
Sigh!
O' dear God!

1742
01:48:07,030 --> 01:48:08,450
And at one such wedding,

1743
01:48:08,660 --> 01:48:10,200
I saw her for the first time.

1744
01:48:11,620 --> 01:48:13,200
She wasn't like the other girls 

1745
01:48:13,220 --> 01:48:15,130
whom I'd forget immediately
after clicking them.

1746
01:48:15,280 --> 01:48:17,070
-Nithya!
-Her face...

1747
01:48:17,280 --> 01:48:18,490
Nithya!

1748
01:48:18,740 --> 01:48:20,160
It pierced right into my heart.

1749
01:48:21,370 --> 01:48:24,160
Many years after Darshana,

1750
01:48:24,200 --> 01:48:27,200
I couldn't take my eyes off a girl.

1751
01:48:28,280 --> 01:48:29,280
Nithya.

1752
01:48:32,370 --> 01:48:36,040
[Nagumo a Carnatic composition
by Shri Tyagaraja]

1753
01:49:23,200 --> 01:49:24,530
-Come, sis'.
-I'll come later.

1754
01:49:24,910 --> 01:49:26,530
-Come on!
-I'll come later.

1755
01:49:26,530 --> 01:49:27,570
Come on!

1756
01:49:27,700 --> 01:49:29,070
Fine, don't come!
So much attitude!

1757
01:49:33,070 --> 01:49:35,240
I can send the photos on WhatsApp
if you want them.

1758
01:49:35,410 --> 01:49:38,530
Aww! Nice try to get my number!

1759
01:49:40,570 --> 01:49:41,570
Mail them to me.

1760
01:49:42,910 --> 01:49:44,870
If you won't mind,
may I say something?

1761
01:49:45,120 --> 01:49:46,120
Okay.

1762
01:49:46,450 --> 01:49:48,780
I didn't like even a single photo
of yours that I clicked.

1763
01:49:50,160 --> 01:49:51,320
You're very beautiful!

1764
01:49:52,450 --> 01:49:53,490
Your eyes,

1765
01:49:53,530 --> 01:49:54,530
your face,

1766
01:49:54,740 --> 01:49:55,740
your smile.

1767
01:49:55,950 --> 01:49:58,120
I haven't been able to capture
any of these correctly.

1768
01:49:59,820 --> 01:50:00,990
-Mail ID?
-Huh?

1769
01:50:00,990 --> 01:50:02,490
Your... email ID?

1770
01:50:02,530 --> 01:50:03,530
Yeah.

1771
01:50:11,570 --> 01:50:12,990
It was lovely meeting you, Nithya.

1772
01:50:13,620 --> 01:50:14,620
I'm Arun.

1773
01:50:19,740 --> 01:50:20,780
What's happening, man?

1774
01:50:22,830 --> 01:50:23,830
Jimmy bro!

1775
01:50:24,870 --> 01:50:26,070
Did you see that girl?

1776
01:50:26,530 --> 01:50:28,530
Yeah, yeah!
I'm seeing everything.

1777
01:50:29,740 --> 01:50:30,950
I'm going to marry her.

1778
01:50:30,990 --> 01:50:32,740
Yeah, right!
Have you seen her?

1779
01:50:32,990 --> 01:50:34,320
A girl like her!

1780
01:50:34,320 --> 01:50:37,030
Do you think boys... that too, the
boys of Kochi, would forsake her?

1781
01:50:37,030 --> 01:50:37,990
Do you really think so?

1782
01:50:37,990 --> 01:50:39,530
She must be committed.
I am sure!

1783
01:50:44,740 --> 01:50:45,820
She's not committed.

1784
01:50:48,320 --> 01:50:53,530
[Nagumo continues]

1785
01:51:17,240 --> 01:51:18,240
Hey!

1786
01:51:18,570 --> 01:51:19,820
Nithya has e-mailed us.

1787
01:51:19,910 --> 01:51:21,700
She showed the photos
we sent to her family.

1788
01:51:21,740 --> 01:51:22,740
Everyone liked it.

1789
01:51:22,780 --> 01:51:25,820
She has asked us if we can cover her
cousin sister's wedding in Chennai.

1790
01:51:25,910 --> 01:51:27,370
Don't miss this work.

1791
01:51:27,450 --> 01:51:29,620
This is the best chance
for you to hit on her.

1792
01:51:39,700 --> 01:51:41,240
Kedar Kamalesh?

1793
01:51:41,660 --> 01:51:42,660
What's wrong?

1794
01:51:59,950 --> 01:52:01,450
We should meet Nithya, in person.

1795
01:52:01,990 --> 01:52:03,240
I can't believe it!

1796
01:52:04,280 --> 01:52:05,870
He seemed like such a nice person.

1797
01:52:07,200 --> 01:52:08,910
I didn't know that
he's this kind of a guy.

1798
01:52:08,950 --> 01:52:10,660
All this happened
when I was in college.

1799
01:52:10,740 --> 01:52:12,490
Maybe, he's a changed man now.

1800
01:52:14,620 --> 01:52:16,780
Ask your family to enquire
about him, once again.

1801
01:52:17,120 --> 01:52:18,530
It's your cousin's life, after all!

1802
01:52:19,780 --> 01:52:21,200
-What are you saying?
-What about lights?

1803
01:52:21,200 --> 01:52:22,620
Lights should be all over the place.

1804
01:52:22,660 --> 01:52:23,660
I'm thinking, Udaipur.

1805
01:52:23,700 --> 01:52:24,950
-That's nice.
-Perfect!

1806
01:52:24,950 --> 01:52:25,990
The palace in Udaipur?

1807
01:52:26,030 --> 01:52:27,910
I want to get married where
Priya Dongre got married.

1808
01:52:27,910 --> 01:52:28,870
I want that too!

1809
