2541
02:32:37,900 --> 02:32:40,480
Shucks!
I missed a millionaire, huh?

2542
02:32:42,690 --> 02:32:43,900
I love you, baby!

2543
02:32:44,110 --> 02:32:45,110
I love you, baby!

2544
