and head to the hotel.

2564
02:33:32,070 --> 02:33:33,280
Darshana, Hi!

2565
02:33:33,280 --> 02:33:34,860
It's so nice to finally meet you!

2566
02:33:34,900 --> 02:33:37,030
I keep watching all your videos.
I mean, I'm a huge fan!

2567
02:33:37,030 --> 02:33:39,620
That video you shot
in Rajasthan, was awesome!

2568
02:33:39,640 --> 02:33:40,420
Thank you.

2569
02:33:40,440 --> 02:33:42,190
And what you've managed
to do for yourself

2570
02:33:42,220 --> 02:33:44,920
in just 6-7 years is just amazing!

2571
02:33:44,940 --> 02:33:47,190
The video you shot
in Punjab was so good.

2572
02:33:47,230 --> 02:33:49,400
-Nithya, that's enough.
